<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .header img { max-width: 150px; }
        .content { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content h1 { color: #0056b3; font-size: 22px; }
        .otp-code { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #0056b3; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px; background-color: #eef5ff; border-radius: 4px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #0056b3; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        a { color: #0056b3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <% if (locals.logoUrl) { %>
                <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Twoem Online Productions Logo">
            <% } else { %>
                <h2>Twoem Online Productions</h2>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= studentName %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account associated with this email address. If you made this request, please use the One-Time Password (OTP) below to proceed.</p>

            <p>Your OTP is:</p>
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>

            <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact us if you have concerns.</p>

            <!-- Optional: Link to the reset page directly, though user usually copies OTP -->
            <!-- <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="button">Reset Your Password</a>
            </p> -->

            <p>Thank you,<br>The Twoem Online Productions Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Twoem Online Productions. All rights reserved.</p>
            <!-- <p><a href="<%= siteUrl %>">Visit our website</a></p> -->
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
